data.title: When Is El Toro Coaster At Great Adventure Re-Opening?

data.text:
Hey Rat Rock Nation… When is El Toro reopening? We’re hearing that the rumor mill is going absolutely crazy on the reopening date for El Toro, that awesome wooden rollercoaster at Six Flags Great Adventure in Jackson, New Jersey.

El Toro was forced to close in June of 2021 after an accident that injured 14 riders resulting in a structural issue for the ride. Since then, engineers have been working to try to get the ride back up and working.

Well, rumor has it that the ride will reopen on June 16th.
